# Software Installation & Task Manager

## Objective
Practice software installation, removal, and process management in Windows 11.

## Tools Used
- Windows 11
- Google Chrome
- Notepad++
- Task Manager
- Event Viewer

## Steps Performed
1. Installed Google Chrome
2. Installed Notepad++
3. Verified installed applications
4. Used Task Manager to monitor resources
5. Ended running processes
6. Uninstalled software
7. Reviewed Event Viewer logs

## Outcome
Successfully managed software installation and removal while learning how to troubleshoot applications using Task Manager.

